    • gestureHandling

      public MapOptions gestureHandling(GestureHandlingType gestureHandling)
      Sets the gestureHandling option, used to control how Google Maps deals with touch screen devices. We offer no warranty as to whether this actually works given that any touch events are being passed through JavaFX WebView to the map, and vital information may be lost in transmission/translation.

      See Google Maps API - Controlling Zoom and Pan

      Parameters:
      gestureHandling -
      Returns:
